{"tid":289899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國母親帶細路噴水池沖涼：咁樣先健康","createTime":"2017-06-19T11:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T11:21:03.000Z","uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1f405da776b217f86f07b5bbdbc598d9ecc215","tid":289899,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"以為小孩這樣玩很涼快，其實隨時出事！前日，因為天氣炎熱，山東淄博不少家長帶着子孩，到當地一商場門前的觀賞噴水池內戲水打鬧，甚至讓他們脫光衣服，當眾裸奔洗澡！<br />\n<br />\n其實，這些從地面上噴出的高壓水柱，以往就曾造成小孩重要部位受傷，或漏電致死的可怕事故。但這些家長卻未有意識到危險，毫不在意地放任小孩嬉鬧，認為「小孩這樣健康」，還稱這樣挺好的，只要周末就來。<br />\n不少網民對此極不贊同，紛紛表示：「電着的時候請記得也要笑的燦爛些」、「我好像記得以前發生過一個事兒，噴泉突然高壓噴水，結果噴死一個」、「那個水不循環，臭臭的」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170619/56844939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170619%2F56844939&d=O23klGfIocB0W2ueYgB4hpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=fa00db51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170619%2F56844939&h=222ce7e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170619/56844939</a>"},{"pid":"79220bda25d5e5bedbe72a8ff8e9ea4209903505","tid":289899,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b0e701846cd604e6d316c70193c0bc354227d4","tid":289899,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"附合國情"},{"pid":"22fa5e3b7135b28485daa821b304ac643ce94351","tid":289899,"uid":75470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"果度佢地自己地方，我理得佢老母係個噴水池度同個仔含撚啦"}]}